    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "Skeletons are the animated bones of the dead, brought to unlife through foul magic. While most skeletons are mindless automatons, they still possess an evil cunning imparted to them by their animating force\u2014a cunning that allows them to wield weapons and wear armor."
        }
    ],
